Blurb::
Select a parmaterization of the lognormal distribution

Description::

Lognormal variables must be parameterized in one of three ways:

- `option_1`: mean and standard deviation
- `option_2`: mean and error factor
- `option_3`: lambda and zeta

This keyword anchors that selection.

